
---

## 🧠 How It Works
- A separate **thread** continuously generates health values
- The UI is updated using `Platform.runLater()` for thread-safe operations
- Alerts are shown if values go out of safe range

---

## 🚦 Safe Range Rules
| Parameter | Normal Range |
|----------|--------------|
| Heart Rate | 60 - 100 bpm |
| Temperature | 36°C - 38°C |
| Oxygen Level | 95% - 100% |

